data.description: Beautiful Fox Hill Farms 3BR/2BA home now available!  Sitting on a corner lot the home features a side entry 2 car garage, fenced backyard, and recently replaced Roof in 2021. Enjoy the large living room with fireplace, spacious dining room, and kitchen.  Breakfast bar, eat in kitchen space, and indoor laundry can help make everyday life more convenient.  The master bedroom has a huge bathroom that includes dual sinks, seperate shower, and garden tub.  The master closet is huge too! Home comes with a quality 1 year warranty plan to cover major appliances and more!  Take a closer look at this property.  Tours available by appointment.
